# Pagination

## Layout
- Flex: `flex items-center justify-between`
- Page info left, navigation buttons right

## Page Info (Left)
- Text: `text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]`
- Format: `"PAGE 1 OF 32"` (uppercase)

## Navigation Buttons (Right)
- Container: `flex items-center gap-2`
- Each button:
  - `px-4 py-2 text-[14px] text-[#101010]`
  - `bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-lg`
  - `hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] transition-colors font-semibold`

```tsx
<div className="flex items-center justify-between">
  <span className="text-[14px] text-[#7e7e7e]">PAGE 1 OF 32</span>
  <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
    <button className="px-4 py-2 text-[14px] text-[#101010] bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] transition-colors font-semibold">
      Prev
    </button>
    <button className="px-4 py-2 text-[14px] text-[#101010] bg-white border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#f5f9fe] transition-colors font-semibold">
      Next
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
```
